Credits: 

Album Cover

	Songwriter – J’La 
	Produced by Radicule  
	Add. Production –  Black Canvas

WhatItDo

	Mixed by J’La

MyWay

	Add. Keyboard – John Cola 
	Guitar – Gabe 
	Mixed by J’La 
	Mastered by J’La 

WhatItDo (Remix)

	Produced by Black Canvas

	Guitar – Matt Jaekel 
	Mixed by J’La 
	Mastered by J’La 
	

This was made at the start of the pandemic and was finished up until the last month. Proud of this to be my genesis piece. 

Every person that buys this token, gets the full project as a link with all of the audio files including track listing and metadata. 

I just want to thank everyone who was apart of this process. Radicule, Cola, Rich, Zach, & Jaekel. I couldn’t have done this without you guys.
